txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Great filth from the insects surrounding Gabilshathûr. Delivery of the items should be made to Avar at the dwarf-outpost.
'This is disgusting, but it burns well, long and hot.'
'The great filth that falls off of the insects around us can fuel fires in our forges for longer periods and get the fires very hot.'
The dwarves at Gabilshathûr await a delivery of great filth to be made to Avar.
Deliver the great filth to Avar at Gabilshathûr in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver great filth from the insects surrounding Gabilshathûr and return it to Avar at the dwarf-outpost.
Wanted: Great filth from the insects surrounding Gabilshathûr.
